---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - xstasis"
  description="About xstasis - a moving archive of dancefloors"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 neon-text">About</h1>

      <div class="prose-dark space-y-6 text-lg">
        <p>
          xstasis is a living archive of club culture. Started as a personal journal to document
          moments on dancefloors across the world, it has evolved into a digital library of
          experiences, spaces, and the music that moves us.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-12 mb-6">The Run</h2>
        <p>
          The Run is a continuously updated log. Each entry captures a moment in time, a feeling,
          a space. It's meant to be raw and immediate, written shortly after the experience while
          the bass is still reverberating in your chest.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-12 mb-6">The Club Wiki</h2>
        <p>
          Not all clubs are created equal. Some spaces transcend the ordinary and become
          institutions, temples, legendary venues that shape the culture. The club pages are
          deep dives into these spaces, documenting their history, their sound, their vibe.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-12 mb-6">The Articles</h2>
        <p>
          Sometimes you need more than a paragraph. The articles section is for longer
          explorations, reflections on the culture, the music, the philosophy of the night.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-12 mb-6">Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          This is not a review site. There are no ratings, no star systems. Every experience
          is subjective, contextual, dependent on a thousand variables that can't be quantified.
          This is simply documentation of a journey through sound.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-500 italic mt-12">
          The archive is always growing. The journey continues.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-neon-cyan">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          Want to share your own experiences or suggest a club to visit?
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            href="mailto:hello@xstasis.org"
            class="text-gray-400 hover:text-neon-cyan transition-colors"
          >
            Email
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
